        "mainbody": "'''''Combat readiness''''' was a spell that enabled the subject to act more rapidly in combat.",
        "Effect": "When the spell was cast, the subject's eyes widened and briefly shone white. Thereafter, until the spell's duration ended in a minute or more, the subject gained an increased reaction time at the beginning of a combat encounter.\n\nThe subject was also better able to defend against adversaries in flanking positions.",
        "Components": "It only required a [[verbal component]]."
